1
00:00:00,487 --> 00:00:08,587
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,762 --> 00:00:16,999
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,237 --> 00:00:19,228
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,242 --> 00:00:26,008
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:26,079 --> 00:00:29,446
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,649 --> 00:00:33,210
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,587 --> 00:00:36,954
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:37,023 --> 00:00:44,452
<i>Dreaming of only "the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,531 --> 00:00:53,667
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,740 --> 00:01:01,772
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:02,015 --> 00:01:08,853
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:08,922 --> 00:01:16,988
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,297 --> 00:01:25,762
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,839 --> 00:01:27,864
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:38,230 --> 00:01:39,754
- <i>Start the operation!</i>
- <i>Start the operation!</i>

16
00:01:40,566 --> 00:01:46,505
<i>Zero Hour!</i>
<i>The Destruction of</i>
<i>the Hidden Leaf Village Begins!</i>

17
00:01:56,915 --> 00:01:57,779
Lord Hokage!

18
00:01:58,450 --> 00:01:59,075
Leave it to me!

19
00:02:02,020 --> 00:02:04,386
Lord Kazekage!
What is going on?

20
00:02:08,861 --> 00:02:09,828
Lord Hokage!

21
00:02:13,532 --> 00:02:14,430
Gaara!

22
00:02:18,170 --> 00:02:19,102
Squad One, above.

23
00:02:19,271 --> 00:02:21,569
Squad Two, below!
Protect the lords!

24
00:02:29,648 --> 00:02:30,546
You're in the way!

25
00:02:47,399 --> 00:02:51,859
Lord Hokage...
Please... flee...

26
00:03:13,058 --> 00:03:14,548
It's finally our time to
come on the scene.

27
00:03:14,993 --> 00:03:17,154
We've been transformed
such a long time.

28
00:03:17,229 --> 00:03:19,925
I'm totally pent up with frustration.

29
00:03:20,332 --> 00:03:22,766
You guys smell all sweaty!

30
00:03:23,001 --> 00:03:25,401
Come on, we're all comrades, right...?

31
00:03:26,638 --> 00:03:27,969
<i>Sound Ninja...!</i>

32
00:03:31,243 --> 00:03:31,971
Raido...

33
00:03:32,778 --> 00:03:34,109
We're heading out to
back up Lord Hokage.

34
00:03:34,179 --> 00:03:35,146
Be careful of any traps!

35
00:03:37,249 --> 00:03:37,840
Do it...

36
00:03:38,951 --> 00:03:39,713
Yes sir!

37
00:03:42,087 --> 00:03:42,985
- Ninja Art!
- Ninja Art!

38
00:03:43,055 --> 00:03:44,147
- Four Flames Formation!
- Four Flames Formation!

39
00:03:54,900 --> 00:03:55,730
Barrier!

40
00:04:05,310 --> 00:04:06,834
Lord Kazekage...

41
00:04:10,549 --> 00:04:12,210
Barrier Ninjutsu, huh?!

42
00:04:13,251 --> 00:04:14,741
To think that they could outwit Anbu...

43
00:04:15,587 --> 00:04:16,884
They're not just ordinary...

44
00:04:20,492 --> 00:04:22,824
What are you doing here?!
Lord Hokage is in danger!

45
00:04:32,871 --> 00:04:35,135
What a nuisance...

46
00:04:35,340 --> 00:04:38,036
To think that the enemy was
masquerading as our Anbu...

47
00:04:39,277 --> 00:04:41,142
So it was also that guy
who used Genjutsu!

48
00:04:41,847 --> 00:04:43,940
Yeah... there's no mistake.

49
00:04:47,252 --> 00:04:48,549
I didn't expect that...

50
00:04:49,254 --> 00:04:51,654
Sand Village would betray Leaf Village.

51
00:04:52,858 --> 00:04:57,488
The treaty is simply a camouflage to
make the enemy let down their guard.

52
00:04:58,096 --> 00:05:00,963
The petty little battle game ends now.

53
00:05:01,867 --> 00:05:04,529
From this point on, the course
of history will change!

54
00:05:06,138 --> 00:05:09,767
Are you saying that
you're starting a war?

55
00:05:10,976 --> 00:05:12,068
That's right.

56
00:05:13,145 --> 00:05:15,705
One should avoid resolution
through armed force

57
00:05:15,881 --> 00:05:19,180
and should rather seek
a solution through negotiations.

58
00:05:20,018 --> 00:05:23,749
There's still time... Lord Kazekage!

59
00:05:28,627 --> 00:05:31,653
Perhaps one gets addicted to
peace as one grows older...

60
00:05:32,731 --> 00:05:34,528
Sarutobi Sensei!

61
00:05:37,803 --> 00:05:39,031
You're...

62
00:05:48,547 --> 00:05:50,105
Just my bad luck...

63
00:05:50,449 --> 00:05:52,110
to have lookout duty
on a day like this.

64
00:05:52,851 --> 00:05:55,786
I wanted to watch Chunin Exam too.

65
00:05:56,254 --> 00:05:57,221
Stop fussing.

66
00:05:57,522 --> 00:05:59,683
The Chunin Exam takes
place twice a year.

67
00:05:59,958 --> 00:06:01,619
You'll have many more chances
to see it.

68
00:06:01,960 --> 00:06:05,987
But this year, that kid from
the Uchiha Clan is taking part, right?

69
00:06:06,198 --> 00:06:07,859
And I won't have
a chance to see that...

70
00:06:08,667 --> 00:06:10,328
I won't be able to die peacefully.

71
00:06:12,471 --> 00:06:13,096
What's that?!

72
00:06:29,387 --> 00:06:31,446
It's time! Begin!

73
00:06:39,598 --> 00:06:41,998
The Summoning has succeeded.

74
00:06:46,771 --> 00:06:47,760
Huge boa!

75
00:06:48,206 --> 00:06:49,833
Notify Lord Hokage immediately!

76
00:07:06,691 --> 00:07:07,658
I'm not letting you in the village!

77
00:07:21,072 --> 00:07:22,061
Dispatch the reinforcements immediately!

78
00:07:22,340 --> 00:07:22,897
Yes sir!

79
00:07:35,987 --> 00:07:36,817
Sand Ninja!

80
00:07:41,993 --> 00:07:43,290
What's going on?

81
00:07:44,029 --> 00:07:44,893
Stop that, Gaara!

82
00:07:46,865 --> 00:07:49,390
I'll kill him...!

83
00:07:51,970 --> 00:07:54,302
There's no meaning in
continuing this fight!

84
00:07:54,372 --> 00:07:56,033
Don't forget our mission!

85
00:07:57,709 --> 00:07:58,437
Out of my way...!

86
00:08:00,779 --> 00:08:02,337
What are you guys doing?!

87
00:08:03,081 --> 00:08:05,140
The operation is already underway!

88
00:08:19,798 --> 00:08:21,993
What in the world is going on?

89
00:08:25,036 --> 00:08:25,695
Gaara!

90
00:08:27,272 --> 00:08:28,000
What's the matter?!

91
00:08:31,076 --> 00:08:32,509
His wound is deeper than
I thought!

92
00:08:33,211 --> 00:08:35,771
And moreover his Chakra
is pretty drained!

93
00:08:36,248 --> 00:08:38,079
In that case,
what about using that thing...?

94
00:08:38,984 --> 00:08:40,042
That's impossible to do right away!

95
00:08:40,385 --> 00:08:42,683
Idiot! It's all because
you didn't wait for the signal

96
00:08:42,754 --> 00:08:44,915
and tried to become
the Perfect Possession...

97
00:08:45,156 --> 00:08:46,680
What should we do?!

98
00:08:47,125 --> 00:08:48,717
Are you saying we have to do
this without Gaara?

99
00:09:02,007 --> 00:09:03,201
Isn't Gaara here yet?!

100
00:09:09,648 --> 00:09:12,549
Gaara is Sand's trump card.

101
00:09:13,251 --> 00:09:16,049
We have to get Gaara to do his work,
no matter what!

102
00:09:16,821 --> 00:09:20,382
You guys leave for the moment and
tend to Gaara's wounds!

103
00:09:21,159 --> 00:09:23,218
As soon as Gaara's Chakra has
been restored...

104
00:09:23,561 --> 00:09:25,153
the operation will recommence!

105
00:09:25,897 --> 00:09:26,625
Got it!

106
00:09:29,801 --> 00:09:30,699
What about you, Sensei?!

107
00:09:31,236 --> 00:09:33,295
I'm gonna suppress those guys!

108
00:09:35,106 --> 00:09:38,234
Do you think things will
go according to your plan?

109
00:09:39,644 --> 00:09:41,942
I'll make them so...

110
00:09:57,562 --> 00:09:58,221
Go!

111
00:09:59,597 --> 00:10:00,120
Okay!

112
00:10:07,672 --> 00:10:10,732
Is Orochimaru the host of this party?

113
00:10:12,577 --> 00:10:17,378
Dunno... In any case,
let's heat this thing up.

114
00:10:24,422 --> 00:10:25,320
Sasuke...

115
00:10:27,025 --> 00:10:30,688
Sorry, but the Chunin Exam ends here.

116
00:10:32,797 --> 00:10:34,822
You've already achieved Chunin level.

117
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:38,963
If you're a Leaf Shinobi,
be of service to the Leaf!

118
00:10:40,338 --> 00:10:43,102
In other words, I'm supposed to
take down that jerk Gaara, right?

119
00:10:43,375 --> 00:10:44,808
A continuation of earlier on, right?

120
00:10:45,176 --> 00:10:46,370
Don't pursue too far.

121
00:10:46,678 --> 00:10:49,613
From here on, it's no longer an exam.
It's the real thing!

122
00:10:50,548 --> 00:10:52,709
What I have to do though...
is the same!

123
00:10:54,719 --> 00:10:55,686
I won't let him through!

124
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:10,098
<i>Sasuke...!</i>

125
00:11:12,804 --> 00:11:13,964
Boy oh boy...

126
00:11:14,506 --> 00:11:18,943
We intended to take Sasuke
while Gaara was causing the trouble.

127
00:11:19,978 --> 00:11:23,812
But not everything goes as planned.

128
00:11:25,517 --> 00:11:28,486
I see... Is that so?

129
00:11:29,487 --> 00:11:34,618
So Leaf Village and...
Sasuke were the target, huh?

130
00:11:35,527 --> 00:11:38,018
Is the Leaf such a big catch?

131
00:11:38,930 --> 00:11:42,832
More importantly,
if Gaara wakes up,

132
00:11:42,967 --> 00:11:46,061
I'll be able to show you something
much more interesting.

133
00:11:46,504 --> 00:11:48,165
Well, anyway...

134
00:11:48,807 --> 00:11:52,538
Your thick-headedness has caused
the Leaf to be outmaneuvered.

135
00:11:53,411 --> 00:11:55,038
It's <i>my</i> win.

136
00:11:56,681 --> 00:11:59,809
Nothing is decided
until the very end.

137
00:12:00,351 --> 00:12:02,683
I believe that's what I taught you...

138
00:12:11,863 --> 00:12:13,296
Orochimaru.

139
00:12:18,570 --> 00:12:22,597
I thought this day would
eventually arrive.

140
00:12:23,641 --> 00:12:24,665
However...

141
00:12:25,844 --> 00:12:29,507
You won't get my head that easily!

142
00:12:31,282 --> 00:12:32,749
I told you, didn't I?

143
00:12:33,117 --> 00:12:36,678
It is preferable to decide
the Fifth Hokage quickly...

144
00:12:37,288 --> 00:12:38,619
Third Hokage...

145
00:12:39,424 --> 00:12:43,190
because you will... die here.

146
00:13:00,178 --> 00:13:03,272
<i>I wonder how the Chunin Exams</i>
<i>are going?</i>

147
00:13:04,282 --> 00:13:06,978
<i>I wonder if Naruto's match is over yet?</i>

148
00:13:08,453 --> 00:13:11,013
<i>The first match was</i>
<i>with Neji, right?</i>

149
00:13:12,457 --> 00:13:14,425
<i>I want him to win that</i>
<i>match somehow or other.</i>

150
00:13:15,127 --> 00:13:16,151
That's no good!

151
00:13:16,394 --> 00:13:18,555
A teacher mustn't root for
one particular student!

152
00:13:18,630 --> 00:13:20,564
All the graduating students
are dear to him!

153
00:13:20,632 --> 00:13:22,463
I must root for all of them equally!

154
00:13:26,872 --> 00:13:31,206
<i>But I still...want Naruto to win...</i>

155
00:13:32,244 --> 00:13:34,178
Are you worried about Naruto?

156
00:13:34,246 --> 00:13:35,804
Well, of course...!

157
00:13:38,016 --> 00:13:39,142
As I thought...

158
00:13:40,619 --> 00:13:42,610
Y-You guys...

159
00:13:43,989 --> 00:13:46,321
I told you to do ten laps around
the school grounds, didn't I?!

160
00:13:46,892 --> 00:13:48,757
We finished that long ago.

161
00:13:49,194 --> 00:13:51,526
While you were daydreaming, Sensei.

162
00:13:53,632 --> 00:13:57,329
When our teacher is in that state,
he can't teach a class!

163
00:13:57,669 --> 00:13:59,864
So let's call it quits for today!

164
00:14:00,071 --> 00:14:03,563
N-No, no!
I'm continuing with class.

165
00:14:07,012 --> 00:14:08,877
I wonder what that smoke is...?

166
00:14:11,149 --> 00:14:12,878
That's coming from the direction
of the exam arena...

167
00:14:15,420 --> 00:14:17,718
Isn't there some disturbance
to the east?

168
00:14:18,657 --> 00:14:20,682
I wonder if something happened?

169
00:14:26,131 --> 00:14:27,223
That Orochimaru...

170
00:14:28,133 --> 00:14:28,929
What should we do?

171
00:14:29,100 --> 00:14:30,624
Should we send reinforcements?

172
00:14:30,969 --> 00:14:34,234
No... It's dangerous to make a move
when we don't really know

173
00:14:34,306 --> 00:14:35,432
what the situation is.

174
00:14:35,774 --> 00:14:38,242
If the mastermind is Orochimaru...

175
00:14:38,510 --> 00:14:39,408
even more so.

176
00:14:41,046 --> 00:14:44,846
Is Orochimaru...
that dangerous a guy?

177
00:14:45,884 --> 00:14:49,786
Originally... he was a student
of the Third Hokage.

178
00:14:50,355 --> 00:14:52,880
So why did he become a Rogue Ninja?

179
00:14:53,858 --> 00:14:57,919
Long ago, when the Fourth Hokage
was decided...

180
00:14:59,030 --> 00:15:02,693
Orochimaru apparently asserted that
he was capable of taking on that role.

181
00:15:03,835 --> 00:15:05,166
But his request was denied.

182
00:15:06,905 --> 00:15:09,999
And shortly afterwards,
that guy slipped out of this village

183
00:15:10,942 --> 00:15:13,206
Orochimaru most likely holds
a grudge against

184
00:15:13,278 --> 00:15:15,041
the Third Hokage because of that.

185
00:15:16,314 --> 00:15:17,713
Revenge... is it?

186
00:15:18,183 --> 00:15:19,150
Probably.

187
00:15:20,685 --> 00:15:22,414
Long ago, when I was a kid...

188
00:15:23,755 --> 00:15:27,191
there's one thing I remember
thinking when I saw that guy...

189
00:15:32,697 --> 00:15:34,824
That he didn't seem human...

190
00:15:35,500 --> 00:15:38,663
That he seems to be something
that just took on a human form...

191
00:15:40,772 --> 00:15:41,761
Frightening...

192
00:15:43,708 --> 00:15:46,438
Simply... frightening.

193
00:15:50,248 --> 00:15:50,976
Reporting

194
00:15:51,850 --> 00:15:53,909
A large boa has appeared near
the eastern gate of the Leaf Village!

195
00:15:54,386 --> 00:15:57,787
And behind it, some one hundred
Sand Ninja are infiltrating the country!

196
00:15:58,290 --> 00:16:00,258
They are currently engaged in
armed conflict with our Shinobi

197
00:16:00,325 --> 00:16:01,053
who were patrolling nearby!

198
00:16:01,993 --> 00:16:02,789
<i>The Sand...?!</i>

199
00:16:05,430 --> 00:16:08,058
Leave Squad One and Two behind
and make for the eastern gate.

200
00:16:08,366 --> 00:16:08,855
Immediately!

201
00:16:09,301 --> 00:16:09,892
- Yes sir!
- Yes sir!

202
00:16:21,346 --> 00:16:23,075
We won't let you past this point!

203
00:16:38,830 --> 00:16:40,297
There's quite a large number.

204
00:16:40,465 --> 00:16:41,591
We were careless!

205
00:16:42,067 --> 00:16:44,035
And even Lord Hokage has been...

206
00:16:45,570 --> 00:16:48,266
Kakashi! Look inside the Barrier!

207
00:16:48,773 --> 00:16:49,364
Yeah.

208
00:16:50,041 --> 00:16:50,871
<i>What...?</i>

209
00:16:57,382 --> 00:16:58,076
Orochimaru!

210
00:16:59,851 --> 00:17:00,715
Orochimaru?!

211
00:17:02,520 --> 00:17:03,612
<i>Why is that guy...?</i>

212
00:17:05,190 --> 00:17:07,181
<i>Don't tell me that</i>
<i>they're after Sasuke again?!</i>

213
00:17:09,027 --> 00:17:09,789
Sasuke!

214
00:17:12,130 --> 00:17:12,892
<i>Huh?</i>

215
00:17:13,798 --> 00:17:14,992
<i>He's not there...?</i>

216
00:17:27,846 --> 00:17:30,371
Sakura, stay there for a while.

217
00:17:31,216 --> 00:17:32,410
I'm gonna go reduce
the number of enemies.

218
00:18:03,748 --> 00:18:06,740
Darn! I'm worried about
Lord Hokage, but...

219
00:18:07,385 --> 00:18:08,545
Leave above to Anbu.

220
00:18:09,254 --> 00:18:10,152
Besides...

221
00:18:10,622 --> 00:18:14,183
Lord Hokage isn't the kind of guy
who can be taken down that easily.

222
00:18:15,794 --> 00:18:16,385
But...

223
00:18:17,328 --> 00:18:22,561
After all, he <i>is</i> the Hokage
the Village Hidden in the Leaves.

224
00:18:32,911 --> 00:18:36,005
Are you so happy, you're crying?

225
00:18:37,048 --> 00:18:37,980
Or...

226
00:18:38,783 --> 00:18:45,848
do you have an iota of sadness
in your heart to kill me, your teacher?

227
00:18:47,692 --> 00:18:48,454
No...

228
00:19:05,343 --> 00:19:07,641
Since earlier on, I was feeling so sleepy...

229
00:19:07,912 --> 00:19:09,971
but I'm finally awake.

230
00:19:11,816 --> 00:19:14,444
That's what I thought.

231
00:19:18,723 --> 00:19:23,217
I know you aren't someone
who would hold a grudge.

232
00:19:23,561 --> 00:19:27,122
You have neither a goal nor motive.

233
00:19:27,532 --> 00:19:29,830
Hmm... I guess...

234
00:19:30,668 --> 00:19:33,068
I <i>do</i> kind of have a goal.

235
00:19:33,838 --> 00:19:35,465
If I were to explain it...

236
00:19:36,841 --> 00:19:40,106
It's interesting to watch things
that move.

237
00:19:40,912 --> 00:19:44,143
I get no pleasure if
something doesn't move.

238
00:19:44,916 --> 00:19:47,077
Like a windmill that doesn't turn...

239
00:19:47,619 --> 00:19:51,521
Well, it may have some kind
of appeal once in a while.

240
00:19:51,823 --> 00:19:54,519
But usually,
it's not worth looking at it.

241
00:19:55,860 --> 00:19:59,956
Right now... with a wind called
"Destroy the Leaf Village

242
00:20:00,031 --> 00:20:02,556
I want to turn that windmill.

243
00:20:04,936 --> 00:20:07,302
You're the same as always...

244
00:20:24,856 --> 00:20:25,618
Sakura!

245
00:20:27,392 --> 00:20:30,225
It was worth teaching you Genjutsu
survival training

246
00:20:30,295 --> 00:20:31,785
during the Genin Exam.

247
00:20:32,530 --> 00:20:35,260
You truly have a talent for it.

248
00:20:35,800 --> 00:20:36,357
Huh?

249
00:20:37,502 --> 00:20:40,437
Release the Genjutsu and
wake up Naruto and Shikamaru!

250
00:20:46,110 --> 00:20:48,135
Naruto will be delighted.

251
00:20:49,247 --> 00:20:50,544
He'll be getting a mission
after such a long while.

252
00:20:52,250 --> 00:20:53,376
What do you mean by a mission?

253
00:20:54,152 --> 00:20:55,517
Be careful...

254
00:20:57,255 --> 00:21:00,247
It's the first A ranked mission
since the Land of the Waves.

255
00:21:05,898 --> 00:21:15,967
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

256
00:21:16,408 --> 00:21:27,251
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

257
00:21:37,362 --> 00:21:42,994
<i>Yes, breathe in the air</i>
<i>Lift your face to the sky and jump</i>

258
00:21:43,068 --> 00:21:48,028
<i>If it rains, take a break</i>
<i>Go where the wind takes you</i>

259
00:21:48,407 --> 00:21:53,310
<i>So many regrets</i>
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>

260
00:21:53,378 --> 00:21:58,509
<i>Let's go carve the badges in our chest</i>
<i>Yes, it's Show Time, life begins now.</i>

261
00:21:58,583 --> 00:22:08,754
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

262
00:22:09,061 --> 00:22:19,494
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

263
00:22:19,571 --> 00:22:30,140
<i>Transform sadness into the wind</i>
<i>and continue to forge on</i>

264
00:22:30,215 --> 00:22:35,778
<i>Forge on strong</i>

265
00:22:47,767 --> 00:22:50,998
Yes! I've been waiting for this!

266
00:22:51,304 --> 00:22:54,034
Finally, it's the first A Ranked mission
in a while!

267
00:22:54,240 --> 00:22:55,867
Listen, Sakura and Shikamaru!

268
00:22:55,942 --> 00:22:58,638
As long as I'm with you,
it will be an easy one.

269
00:22:58,878 --> 00:23:01,403
I'm the super hero who
can wake a sleeping lion.

270
00:23:01,481 --> 00:23:06,714
Just keep watching
Mr. Naruto's stellar performance!

271
00:23:07,353 --> 00:23:10,686
Next time: "Village in Distress:
A New A Ranked Mission!"

272
00:23:10,890 --> 00:23:12,653
Let's go! Let's go! Let's go
